com.rikdata.ppl.common.form

Annotation Type EntityType


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface EntityType

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      boolean noLineActions
      (Optional) noLineActions entities dont show any action buttons (such as add new line, delete line, copy line) in the webform
      boolean noteBookDisabled
      (Optional) AdvanceEntityService always try to find notebooks for all entities when searched for webform.
      boolean showCopyBtn 
      boolean showDeleteBtn 
      boolean showEditBtn 
      boolean showViewBtn 
      boolean viewOnly
      (Optional) read only fields are always present as read only in the form and user entered values ignore during save
